    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_03",
      "start_sec": 3.66,
      "duration": 1.92,
      "text": "3日間の軽度な睡眠不足でも、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 緊張 (tension)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_04",
      "start_sec": 5.58,
      "duration": 1.74,
      "text": "前頭前野の活動が低下し、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 緊張 (tension)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_05",
      "start_sec": 7.32,
      "duration": 1.79,
      "text": "感情の制御がうまくできなくなる。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 怒り (anger)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_06",
      "start_sec": 9.11,
      "duration": 0.91,
      "text": "怒りやすくなる、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 怒り (anger)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_07",
      "start_sec": 10.02,
      "duration": 1.7,
      "text": "自分勝手な言動が増えるなど、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 怒り (anger)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_08",
      "start_sec": 11.71,
      "duration": 1.57,
      "text": "“性格が変わったように見える”",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_09",
      "start_sec": 13.28,
      "duration": 2.22,
      "text": "行動はただの寝不足が原因かもしれない。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_10",
      "start_sec": 15.5,
      "duration": 2.36,
      "text": "慢性寝不足は“脳の一部を失う”",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_11",
      "start_sec": 17.86,
      "duration": 1.64,
      "text": "慢性的な睡眠不足では、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_12",
      "start_sec": 19.5,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "グリア細胞がシナプスを除去し始め、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_13",
      "start_sec": 21.54,
      "duration": 1.38,
      "text": "神経回路の一部が",
